<lb ed="X" n="0749b23"/><p id="pX63p0749b2301" rend="margin-left:1em">共功<figure entity="FigX63074915"/>臣用　<figure entity="FigX63074916"/>化生　臣向君。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0749b24"/><p id="pX63p0749b2401" rend="margin-left:1em">功功<figure entity="FigX63074917"/>不動　<figure entity="FigX63074918"/>內生　君向臣。</p>
<pb ed="X" id="X63.1256.0749c" n="0749c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0749c01"/><p id="pX63p0749c0101" rend="margin-left:1em">正中偏夜深古殿&CB02083;輕&CB00195;寂寂苔封臣不立密密
<lb ed="X" n="0749c02"/>光舒未兆前。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0749c03"/><p id="pX63p0749c0301" rend="margin-left:1em">偏中正玉人不親臨臺鏡子夜星沉瑞氣濃依舊
<lb ed="X" n="0749c04"/>青山不露頂。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0749c05"/><p id="pX63p0749c0501" rend="margin-left:1em">正中來木人&CB00234;杖火中回&CB01904;起泥牛耕練色放教
<lb ed="X" n="0749c06"/>石馬踐蒼苔。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0749c07"/><p id="pX63p0749c0701" rend="margin-left:1em">偏中至轉側相逢全意氣交輝終不犯鋒芒大用
<lb ed="X" n="0749c08"/><anchor id="fnX63p0749c03"/>蹤橫無變異。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0749c09"/><p id="pX63p0749c0901" rend="margin-left:1em">兼中到明暗盡時光不照石人有志妙難窮鮮栽
<lb ed="X" n="0749c10"/>絕頂無根草。</p></def></entry>
